            (p [This is my main pet project currently. A more detailed description can be found ,(where-to-find "posts/this-site.html")])
            (p [This should be my personal website, built without me writing any HTML. Serves as a break from developing complete full-stack stuff. 
            It can also be used to pass the time, as I'm writing it litle by little at the moment, figuring stuff out as I go.]))))

